:"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-prays-after-friday-in-his-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":41209,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Friday: The Prophet prays after Friday in his house","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not pray after Friday prayer until he had departed and thus would pray in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 895, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 882 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36158,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/13\/two-nawafil-before-maghrib\/","url_meta":{"origin":41209,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Recommended voluntary prayer before Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: We used to prayer two cycles after the sun set before sunset prayer in the time of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. It was said to him, \u201cDid the Messenger of Allah pray both of them?\u201d Anas said, \u201cThe Prophet saw us praying\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","blo